item.title: BEST OF 2023
item.description: We're back this week with our long-awaited Best of 2023 episode and there's a lot for you to wrap your ears around. In a time that many seem all-too-thrilled to declare the death of a genre, there was an increasing number of great albums and songs released in 2023. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/decibelgeek
